NAME

    File::Open - wrap open/sysopen/opendir and give them a nice and simple
    interface

INSTALLATION

    To install this module, run the following commands:

        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make test
        make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

    After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
    perldoc command.

        perldoc File::Open

    You can also look for information at:

    *   RT, CPAN's request tracker:
        <https://rt.cpan.org/Dist/Display.html?Name=File-Open>

    *   MetaCPAN: <https://metacpan.org/pod/File::Open>

